response.overview: On December 02, 2017, Osaka Central Gymnasium Sub Arena in Osaka hosted Day 12 of NJPW World Tag League 2017, broadcast on Samurai! TV. The main event featured CHAOS (Kazuchika Okada, Will Ospreay & Gedo) vs Los Ingobernables de Japon (EVIL & SANADA). The card also featured BULLET CLUB (Tama Tonga & Tanga Loa) vs Juice Robinson & David Finlay. Other wrestlers on the show include Tomoyuki Oka, Minoru Suzuki, and Bad Luck Fale, and more!
response.title: NJPW World Tag League 2017: Day 12
